Output docs/ui/spike-screenshots/opentui-spike-portrait.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontFamily "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font Mono"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1100
Set Height 1600
Set Padding 10
Set TypingSpeed 20ms

Type "cd '/Volumes/SumoDeus NVMe/openclaw/workspace/worktrees/sumocode-yoga'"
Enter
Sleep 200ms

Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 100ms

Type "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY= ANTHROPIC_OAUTH_TOKEN= pi --offline --model google/gemini-2.5-flash --no-extensions --no-skills --no-prompt-templates --no-themes --no-context-files --no-session -e ./src/opentui-spike-extension.ts"
Enter
Sleep 8s

Screenshot docs/ui/spike-screenshots/opentui-splash-portrait.png

Ctrl+D
Sleep 500ms
Type "asd"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Screenshot docs/ui/spike-screenshots/opentui-exit-clean-portrait.png
Ctrl+D
Sleep 300ms
